Package: geofacet
Title: ggplot2 faceting utilities for geographical data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Ryan", "Hafen", email = "rhafen@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides geofaceting functionality for ggplot2. Geofaceting arranges a sequence of plots of data for different geographical entities into a grid that preserves some of the geographical orientation.
Depends: R (>= 3.3.2)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    ggplot2,
    gtable,
    graphics
Suggests:
    testthat,
    covr,
    lintr
